Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:45.79,jansa,,0,0,0,,Os fragmentos dos nossos sonhos se fundiram em um.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:43.52,Credits,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(858,345)}Edição\N{\fs40}Sewil
